snippet.title: Hyperspace Pinball For Steam - Prototype
snippet.description:
Intended release: September 2015
Official page: http://www.gamieon.com/hyperspacepinball
Twitter: @gamieon
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/HyperspacePinball

Defend the solar system from an alien invasion using a light ball and flippers as your weapon. Rack up big points, achievements and leaderboard rankings as you take skill shots, conquer mini-challenges, defeat bosses, build your jackpot and destroy every alien in your path.
